divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside playing basketball with my cousin when he pointed out a hovering disk-shaped object in the sky.I thought it was a plane at first but it was just hovering in the same spot for about a minute. Then It started to slowly hover away into the distance .A few minutes later it stoped then quickly accelerated away.
